WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Tap "Browse Brands" and search 150+ Pakistani brands.

00:06.000 --> 00:14.000
Open a brand — here, Baroque's official store.

00:14.000 --> 00:24.000
Browse its categories and pick a product you love.

00:24.000 --> 00:34.000
Prefer the Pakistani site for real PKR (some show higher USD).

00:34.000 --> 00:44.000
Copy the product link and paste it into PakPoshak.

00:44.000 --> 00:54.000
It reads the item and shows your estimated total in BDT.

00:54.000 --> 01:03.000
Add another product, or continue to your details.

01:03.000 --> 01:14.000
Enter your name, WhatsApp number, and delivery address.

01:14.000 --> 01:26.000
Review your full order summary and the all-in total.

01:26.000 --> 01:36.000
Tap Confirm & Submit — you get an Order ID to track.

01:36.000 --> 01:52.000
Pay with bKash, Nagad, Upay or Rocket using the details shown.

01:52.000 --> 02:08.000
Already paid? Enter the amount, method, and TrxID.

02:08.000 --> 02:22.000
Upload your payment screenshot to confirm.

02:22.000 --> 02:30.000
Done! We only WhatsApp you if something's out of stock.
